core::sync::atomic::AtomicBool::new.doc:
Creates a new `AtomicBool`.

# Examples

```
use std::sync::atomic::AtomicBool;

let atomic_true = AtomicBool::new(true);
let atomic_false = AtomicBool::new(false);
```

